                    </h3>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/kainos/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline border-blue-300 text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-600 hover:text-white hover:border-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center space-x-2">
